OL,3,CJersey patients 'bed block' for total
OL,4,Cof nearly 5,000 days in 2025
OL,6,FPatients were forced to spend a total
OL,7,Fof 4,922 days in beds at Jersey's
OL,8,FGeneral Hospital during 2025, due to a
OL,9,Flack of ongoing care provision.
OL,11,FFigures obtained by ITV Channel
OL,12,Fthrough a Freedom of Information
OL,13,Frequest (FOI) reveal that these people
OL,14,Fwere medically fit to leave but had to
OL,15,Fstay as they waited for spaces in
OL,16,Fother care facilities or for a support
OL,17,Fpackage to allow them to return home.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784231285
OL,3,CJersey patients 'bed block' for total
OL,4,Cof nearly 5,000 days in 2025
OL,6,FJersey's Health Minister, Senator Tom
OL,7,FBinet, says: "Some of that's long term
OL,8,Fbecause we haven't got enough dementia
OL,9,Fbeds and there's a slight shortage of
OL,10,Fcare home beds in certain incidences.
OL,12,F"That can only really be addressed
OL,13,Fwhen we've got more provision and the
OL,14,FHealth Village really needs to be
OL,15,Fmoved forward as quickly as we can.
OL,17,F"In the short term, I know the
OL,18,FPartnership Board are doing work to
OL,19,Fsee if we can increase community
OL,20,Fprovision to try and ease the
OL,21,Fsituation."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784231285
OL,3,CJersey patients 'bed block' for total
OL,4,Cof nearly 5,000 days in 2025
OL,6,FThe proposed Health Village in St
OL,7,FSaviour is part of the Government's
OL,8,F#710 million plan to improve the
OL,9,Fisland's healthcare facilities and
OL,10,Fcapacity - including a new Acute
OL,11,FHospital at Overdale.
OL,13,FFigures from a separate ITV Channel
OL,14,FFOI request show that only 101 'bed
OL,15,Fdays' were taken up at the hospital
OL,16,Flast year due to a patient or family
OL,17,Fmember choosing to postpone their
OL,18,Fdischarge when they were medically fit
OL,19,Fto leave.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784231285
OL,3,CJersey patients 'bed block' for total
OL,4,Cof nearly 5,000 days in 2025
OL,6,FThis number has however almost tripled
OL,7,Fsince 2024, which in itself was almost
OL,8,Ftriple the 2023 figure.
OL,10,FOther reasons listed for delays not
OL,11,Frelated to someone's care in 2025 were
OL,12,Fhousing and finances, with 388 and 131
OL,13,Fextra 'bed days' respectively.
OL,15,FIn March, Senator Binet announced that
OL,16,Fadult patients would be charged #502
OL,17,Ffor each day they stay in hospital
OL,18,Funnecessarily - with a grace period
OL,19,Fand some caveats for personal
OL,20,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784231285
OL,3,CJersey patients 'bed block' for total
OL,4,Cof nearly 5,000 days in 2025
OL,6,FSince that rule was brought in, no one
OL,7,Ffaced a bill and the Minister adds:
OL,8,F"It was never a means to increase
OL,9,Frevenue, it was really to try and get
OL,10,Fbehavioural change.
OL,12,F"The very fact that's now law has
OL,13,Fmeant people who would otherwise have
OL,14,Fstayed have decided to move on, which
OL,15,Fis freeing up hospital beds so it's
OL,16,Fworking well."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
